title: Monsoon India
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Indian restaurant at Menehune Shores with 9-item vegetarian section, several of which are vegan suitable - ask. Buffet contains vegetarian items on a different side of the table from meat-containing items. Mon-Thur lunch special comes with a vegetarian (or non-veg) dish, lentils, small salad, basmati rice, and naan. Ocean view seating.
